Our Android Application, "HELP', is an app designed to help people in distress due to any reason. "HELP" allows a user to 
alert his/her near and dear ones about him/her being in an uncomfortable situation or if he/she is facing some kind of medical 
emergency.

"HELP" assists you during your travel as well and allows you to share your vehicle number and type of vehicle you are commuting 
in to your dear ones!

If the user faces some trouble, then he/she can press the SOS or Medical Emergency Button tapping which an alert SMS is sent to 
all the people present in the guardian list created by the user along with the deatils of the vehicle in which the user and
travelling and his/her precise GPS location.
